{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08@4.pkg/1772602072149/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602073001", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08@4.pkg/1772602072149/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602073001"}, "identifier": "58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A.有误，应该是“比中见兴”，而不是“赋中见兴”的手法</span></p>\n</div>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对《蒹葭》赏析有误的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列对《蒹葭》赏析有误的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08@4.pkg/item.json?v=1753227552929", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>“蒹葭苍苍，白露为霜”采用的是“赋中见兴”的手法，为诗歌创设了一种萧瑟、迷茫的意境。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;溯洄从之&rdquo;和&ldquo;溯游从之&rdquo;通过连续匆匆的寻求行动，表现了主人公内心的焦急和痴迷，暗示了&ldquo;伊人&rdquo;踪迹飘忽，难以寻觅。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;蒹葭&rdquo;&ldquo;水&rdquo;和&ldquo;伊人&rdquo;的形象交相辉映，浑然一体，用作起兴的事物与所要描绘的对象形成一个完整的艺术世界。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本诗没有直接抒情，没有叙述主人公对心上人如何思念，而是通过行动含蓄地表现其内心的情感，充满了难言的惆怅和伤感。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对《蒹葭》赏析有误的一项是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "58334c95-4595-41f5-a5ce-e5ff42435a08", 